menuconfig SENSOR_REGISTRY
	bool "Sensor registry (uid → metadata)"
	depends on ZBUS
	help
	  Maintains a runtime map from sensor_uid to human-readable metadata
	  (location label, remote flag). Display and MQTT consumers use the
	  registry rather than hardcoding UIDs. Sensor drivers register
	  themselves during SYS_INIT at APPLICATION priority.
